            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": "Out of the total population of 164,444 in Nepalgunj Sub-metropolitan City, 153,577 people were born in Nepal. Among those born in Nepal, 117,480 were born within this sub-metropolitan city, 6,289 in other local levels of Banke district, 30,808 in other districts, 9,835 were born abroad and currently reside in this city, and for 32 people, the birthplace was not disclosed."
