        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": "Based on the previous place of residence in the last 12 months, out of the total population of 164,444 in the sub-metropolitan city, the highest number, 116,726 (71.0%), are residing in this very municipality, while 8,499 (5.2%) have migrated from other local levels within the same district. Similarly, the number of persons migrating from other districts is 29,429 (17.9%), and those migrating from abroad stands at 9,790 (6.0%)."
